      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FRED THE FOX (1) jumped from an outside draw and finished in the frame when a one length third (25.77) at Warrnambool in Bottom Up - Grade 5. Yet to fire here from two runs. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Can go on with it. SOMERTON WILLOW (6) is better than last start when seventh (26.01) from Box 4 at Sale over 435m. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Key runner on best form. BEELINE (3) scored two back in one of the fastest times on the card then was always well back and could manage only a 11 length 7th at Horsham (24.23) latest. Can do much better this time. PAW CORA (7) has strong claims after a top-three finish at this track and distance last time out.",
